regular expression. Use \\\\'\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\b\\\\' for precise symbol matching (e.g., \\\\'\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\bMatchMe\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\b\\\\').\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n          \\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\"string\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n        },\\\\\\\\n        \\\\\\\\\\\"dir_path\\\\\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\\n          \\\\\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\"Directory or file to search. Directories are searched recursively. Relative paths are resolved against current working directory. Defaults to current working directory (\\\\'.\\\\') if omitted.\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n          \\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\"string\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n        },\\\\\\\\n        \\\\\\\\\\\"include_pattern\\\\\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\\n          \\\\\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\"Glob pattern to filter files (e.g., \\\\'*.ts\\\\', \\\\'src/**\\\\'). Recommended for large repositories to reduce noise. Defaults to all files if omitted.\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n          \\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\"string\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n        },\\\\\\\\n        \\\\\\\\\\\"exclude_pattern\\\\\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\\n          \\\\\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\"Optional: A regular expression pattern to exclude from the search results. If a line matches both the pattern and the exclude_pattern, it will be omitted.\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n          \\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\"string\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n        },'... 57962 more characters,\\n+    retryConfig: {\\n+      retryDelay: 1000,\\n+      retry: 3,\\n+      noResponseRetries: 3,\\n+      statusCodesToRetry: [Array],\\n+      currentRetryAttempt: 0,\\n+      httpMethodsToRetry: [Array],\\n+      retryDelayMultiplier: 2,\\n+      timeOfFirstRequest: 1776821463235,\\n+      totalTimeout: 9007199254740991,\\n+      maxRetryDelay: 9007199254740991\\n+    },\\n+    paramsSerializer: [Function: paramsSerializer],\\n+    validateStatus: [Functi