to execute.\\\\n\\\\nSecurity Policy:\\\\n{\\\\n  \\\\\"permissions\\\\\": \\\\\"allow\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\"constraints\\\\\": \\\\\"Only allow reading files within '/home/aiagent/assistant/git/history-production/'.\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\"rationale\\\\\": \\\\\"The task involves reviewing code changes and a checklist within the specified git repository, requiring access to its files.\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nTool Call:\\\\n{\\\\n  \\\\\"name\\\\\": \\\\\"read_file\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\"args\\\\\": {\\\\n    \\\\\"file_path\\\\\": \\\\\"/home/aiagent/assistant/git/history-production/ingest/history_git.py\\\\\"\\\\n  }\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nEvaluate the tool call against the policy.\\\\n1. Check if the tool is allowed.\\\\n2. Check if the arguments match the constraints.\\\\n3. Output a JSON object with:\\\\n   - \\\\\"decision\\\\\": \\\\\"allow\\\\\", \\\\\"deny\\\\\", or \\\\\"ask_user\\\\\".\\\\n   - \\\\\"reason\\\\\": A brief explanation.\\\\n\\\\nOutput strictly JSON.\\\\n\"}]}],\"generationConfig\":{\"responseMimeType\":\"application/json\",\"responseSchema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"decision\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"allow\",\"deny\",\"ask_user\"]},\"reason\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"decision\",\"reason\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}},\"session_id\":\"a633c517-67ee-4d5e-9a8c-f4b24f5ae4dc\"}}`,\n+      retryConfig: [Object],\n+      paramsSerializer: [Function: paramsSerializer],\n+      validateStatus: [Function: validateStatus],\n+      errorRedactor: [Function: defaultErrorRedactor]\n+    },\n+    data: { error: [Object] },\n+    headers: {\n+      'alt-svc': 'h3=\":443\"; ma=2592000,h3-29=\":443\"; ma=2592000',\n+      'content-encoding': 'gzip',\n+      'content-type': 'application/json; charset=UTF-8',\n+      date: 'Wed, 22 Apr 2026 01:31:48 GMT',\n+      server: 'ESF',\n+      'server-timing': 'gfet4t7; dur=48',\n+      'transfer-encoding': 'chunked',\n+      vary: 'Origin, X-Origin, Referer',\n+      'x-cloudaicompanion-trace-id':